PUTRAJAYA , May 20 - Intan Maizura Othman , the wife of Malaysia Airlines Flight MH370 steward Mohd Hazrin Hasnan , has given birth to a baby boy .
Intan Maizura had uploaded via Instagram , a photograph of her waiting to give birth in Putrajaya Hospital .
Flight MH370 carrying 239 people disappeared from radar screens when flying in the skies over the South China Sea on March 8 after take off from KL International Airport , Sepang at 12.41 midnight .
